p(\boldsymbol{\theta}|\boldsymbol{y})\approx p(\boldsymbol{\theta}|s(\boldsymbol{y})\propto p(s(\boldsymbol{y})|\boldsymbol{\theta})p(\boldsymbol{\theta})
